{"tid":423524,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(慎入長文) 又一個放唔低前度既故事","createTime":"2017-10-04T03:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T07:25:45.000Z","uid":151408,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0468fbcf9046c21c24ef72c551d7790e8631c5c","tid":423524,"uid":151408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:16:39.000Z","msg":"都分左手一個月，聽講佢過得幾好，而相反即使我每日搵好多野做麻醉自己，讀書打機做運動食煙飲酒搵朋友，但始終靜落泥既時候，每分每秒都係諗起同佢既回憶，即使個回憶係好心痛，個腦會逼自己諗，我先知我冇一刻放低過。"},{"pid":"bd4e180792d2620cad9418f15e17bed737b709c1","tid":423524,"uid":62121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"一個月啫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937f6e56dba8a251b8f0e604758a8a6cc31a1f10","tid":423524,"uid":151408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個月啫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同佢都一齊左一個月，我地好辛苦先一齊到，即使好似好短時間，但已經夠我生醉夢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72ab3df1dd9eb8dd481554c024c365fe9052d69","tid":423524,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"放心 過一陣你就唔會咁諗<br />\n人去到最後都會選擇接受"},{"pid":"dfdc00cad38bf2e0ec8cd6f5d185b6f46b14e813","tid":423524,"uid":79570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T07:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一個月啫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同佢都一齊左一個月，我地好辛苦先一齊到，即使好似好短時間，但已經夠我生醉夢死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得1個月就收皮啦"}]}